title: ⬆ Bump upsonic from 0.28.4 to 0.34.3

## Summary by Sourcery Update Upsonic to version 0.34.3. New Features: - Print the user name after the welcome message. Bug Fixes: - Resolve `TypeError` for `list[any]` and `list[int]`. - Fix list typing issues. Enhancements: - Add current datetime in tester mode. - Add comments inside the `dump_module` function. - Add user name print logging after the welcome message. - Add type annotations to functions. - Add print mechanism for exceptions on dump operations. Tests: - Add a try-except block for the get_username function.
